(85, 1, '2020-02-05 05:53:36', '2020-02-05 05:53:36', '<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":6} -->\n<h6>Why not invite our music&nbsp;band, The Redeemed to bring songs, and powerful testimonies to your church, or organisation? Complete the booking form below, and one of our booking staff will be in touch. This is a very dynamic way of&nbsp;bringing along friends and family to hear more about LGMI in partnership with Teen Challenge&amp; others churches &amp; body of Christ</h6>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>The Need</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>With drug abuse problems sweeping Great Britain, many churches throw up their hands in despair. They are searching for strategies to bring the gospel to bear on this plague and resources to come alongside them in this battle. LGMI in partnership with Teen Challenge London is a ministry on the cutting edge and we want you to think of our outreach teams as your resource.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We have such vision for this year, not only to continue our work of residential treatment, counselling, and cooperation with the courts but also in evangelism. We would be more than privileged to bring our men to your church to present a powerful presentation of music, dramatic testimony and challenging ministry from the Bible.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Our team which collectively represents over 50 years of cocaine &amp; heroin abuse, alcoholism, and crime are living miracles. Despite the fact that the name LGMI in partnership with Teen Challenge London implies teenagers, most of the members of this team are in their twenties and thirties. Each has been set free by Jesus and testifies of the miraculous power of Gods saving love. They present dynamic music and a powerful testimony of Gods saving grace. This ministry can have a powerful evangelistic impact for your area.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We do not charge a set fee or minimum. We minister on a love offering basis and are confident that you will not be disappointed. We are reaching out one miracle at a time.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Fill out the form below to arrange&nbsp;a presentation</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Please be sure to include: church name, contact name &amp; telephone number, date and time of presentation and any other information you think may be useful.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Mission Presentation', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'mission-presentation', '', '', '2020-02-05 05:53:36', '2020-02-05 05:53:36', '', 0, 'http://localhost/lgmi_final/?page_id=85', 0, 'page', '', 0),
